<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:itunes="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" xmlns:tts="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#styling" xmlns:amll="http://www.example.com/ns/amll" itunes:timing="Word"><head><metadata><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v1"/><ttm:agent type="other" xml:id="v2"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="Things You Said"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="Things You Said (feat. Abby Cates)"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="Abby Cates"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="Cody Fry"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="Chad Copelin"/><amll:meta key="album" value="The End"/><amll:meta key="album" value="Things You Said"/><amll:meta key="isrc" value="USUM72307288"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="2065868022"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="436716255"/><amll:meta key="spotifyId" value="2k8ZdI4C1ox7duEFJN7BgD"/><amll:meta key="appleMusicId" value="1692622465"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithub" value="96868062"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithubLogin" value="Shomi-FJS"/><iTunesMetadata xmlns="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal"><songwriters><songwriter>Cody Fry</songwriter></songwriters></iTunesMetadata></metadata></head><body dur="3:51.289"><div begin="17.049" end="3:51.289"><p begin="17.049" end="20.186" itunes:key="L1" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="17.049" end="17.240">I</span> <span begin="17.240" end="17.494">was</span> <span begin="17.494" end="17.971">walking</span> <span begin="17.971" end="18.246">in</span> <span begin="18.246" end="18.482">the</span> <span begin="18.482" end="18.943">woods</span> <span begin="18.943" end="19.278">one</span> <span begin="19.401" end="20.186">day</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">某日，我独自漫步于密林深处</span></p><p begin="21.123" end="23.875" itunes:key="L2" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="21.123" end="21.470">Trying</span> <span begin="21.470" end="21.575">to</span> <span begin="21.631" end="21.879">keep</span> <span begin="21.879" end="22.123">the</span> <span begin="22.123" end="22.652">ghosts</span> <span begin="22.652" end="22.954">at</span> <span begin="23.099" end="23.875">bay</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">试图将过往的幽影抵挡在外</span></p><p begin="24.858" end="31.287" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="24.858" end="25.177">Then</span> <span begin="25.177" end="25.269">I</span> <span begin="25.269" end="25.634">thought</span> <span begin="25.634" end="25.766">I</span> <span begin="25.766" end="26.245">saw</span> <span begin="26.245" end="26.584">your</span> <span begin="26.584" end="27.158">face</span> <span begin="27.158" end="27.321">but</span> <span begin="27.321" end="27.552">it</span> <span begin="27.552" end="28.331">was</span> <span begin="28.617" end="29.513">just</span> <span begin="29.513" end="31.287">leaves</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">恍惚间惊见你的容颜，却不过是枝叶摇晃</span></p><p begin="32.035" end="35.075" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="32.035" end="32.217">I</span> <span begin="32.217" end="32.577">see</span> <span begin="32.577" end="32.809">you</span> <span begin="32.809" end="32.974">in</span> <span begin="32.974" end="33.094">the</span> <span begin="33.094" end="34.105">strangest</span> <span begin="34.105" end="35.075">things</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我总在不可思议的事物望见你</span></p><p begin="35.708" end="38.943" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="35.708" end="36.006">Your</span> <span begin="36.006" end="36.329">voice</span> <span begin="36.329" end="36.498">in</span> <span begin="36.498" end="36.781">every</span> <span begin="36.934" end="37.313">bird</span> <span begin="37.402" end="37.685">that</span> <span begin="37.685" end="38.943">sings</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">每一声鸟鸣里，都仿佛藏着你的回响</span></p><p begin="39.677" end="46.165" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="39.677" end="39.944">Can</span> <span begin="39.944" end="40.143">they</span> <span begin="40.143" end="40.517">hear</span> <span begin="40.517" end="40.964">it</span> <span begin="41.020" end="41.869">echoing</span> <span begin="41.869" end="42.164">or</span> <span begin="42.164" end="42.288">is</span> <span begin="42.288" end="42.679">that</span> <span begin="43.380" end="44.288">just</span> <span begin="44.288" end="46.165">me?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">世间万物皆闻此回响，亦或仅是我的一厢情愿？</span></p><p begin="48.001" end="53.472" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="48.001" end="48.271">I</span> <span begin="48.271" end="48.487">don&apos;t</span> <span begin="48.487" end="49.161">believe</span> <span begin="49.161" end="49.536">in</span> <span begin="49.536" end="51.506">haunted</span> <span begin="51.506" end="53.472">houses</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我从不相信世上真有鬼屋</span></p><p begin="54.947" end="58.176" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="54.947" end="55.171">But</span> <span begin="55.171" end="55.283">I</span> <span begin="55.283" end="55.719">still</span> <span begin="55.719" end="56.066">see</span> <span begin="56.066" end="56.276">you</span> <span begin="56.276" end="56.635">there</span> <span begin="56.635" end="56.818">on</span> <span begin="56.818" end="56.935">the</span> <span begin="57.004" end="58.176">bed</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">但我却总瞥见你仍在床畔安眠</span></p><p begin="1:02.712" end="1:08.733" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:02.712" end="1:03.056">You</span> <span begin="1:03.056" end="1:03.457">didn&apos;t</span> <span begin="1:03.457" end="1:03.931">leave</span> <span begin="1:03.931" end="1:04.266">me</span> <span begin="1:04.266" end="1:05.474">much</span> <span begin="1:05.531" end="1:06.132">but</span> <span begin="1:06.348" end="1:06.565">the</span> <span begin="1:06.565" end="1:07.276">things</span> <span begin="1:07.276" end="1:07.837">you</span> <span begin="1:07.837" end="1:08.733">said</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你没有为我留下太多，唯有你的只言片语</span></p><p begin="1:11.276" end="1:16.390" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:11.276" end="1:11.589">They</span> <span begin="1:11.589" end="1:12.492">stayed,</span> <span begin="1:14.917" end="1:15.291">they</span> <span begin="1:15.291" end="1:16.390">stayed</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">久久不散，声声在耳</span></p><p begin="1:23.481" end="1:26.577" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="1:23.481" end="1:23.747">I</span> <span begin="1:23.747" end="1:23.999">was</span> <span begin="1:23.999" end="1:24.422">driving</span> <span begin="1:24.422" end="1:24.666">through</span> <span begin="1:24.666" end="1:24.792">the</span> <span begin="1:24.792" end="1:25.408">streets</span> <span begin="1:25.408" end="1:25.686">one</span> <span begin="1:25.842" end="1:26.577">night</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">某个夜晚，我驱车穿过街巷</span></p><p begin="1:27.194" end="1:30.531" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="1:27.194" end="1:27.371">At</span> <span begin="1:27.441" end="1:27.641">the</span> <span begin="1:27.641" end="1:28.179">corner</span> <span begin="1:28.179" end="1:28.408">with</span> <span begin="1:28.408" end="1:28.632">the</span> <span begin="1:28.632" end="1:29.085">bar</span> <span begin="1:29.085" end="1:29.557">you</span> <span begin="1:29.557" end="1:30.531">like</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">经过你喜欢的那间酒吧拐角</span></p><p begin="1:31.153" end="1:37.881" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="1:31.153" end="1:31.286">I</span> <span begin="1:31.286" end="1:31.613">thought</span> <span begin="1:31.613" end="1:31.735">I</span> <span begin="1:31.735" end="1:32.106">saw</span> <span begin="1:32.106" end="1:32.245">the</span> <span begin="1:32.245" end="1:32.683">car</span> <span begin="1:32.683" end="1:33.180">you</span> <span begin="1:33.180" end="1:33.649">drive</span> <span begin="1:33.649" end="1:33.822">but</span> <span begin="1:33.822" end="1:34.003">it</span> <span begin="1:34.003" end="1:35.294">wasn&apos;t</span> <span begin="1:36.015" end="1:37.881">green</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我以为看见了你的车，可它并不是那抹绿色</span></p><p begin="1:38.563" end="1:41.325" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="1:38.563" end="1:38.738">These</span> <span begin="1:38.738" end="1:39.493">neighborhoods</span> <span begin="1:39.493" end="1:39.695">all</span> <span begin="1:39.695" end="1:40.036">look</span> <span begin="1:40.036" end="1:40.302">the</span> <span begin="1:40.302" end="1:41.325">same</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">这些街区 看起来都千篇一律</span></p><p begin="1:42.233" end="1:45.216" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="1:42.233" end="1:42.483">That&apos;s</span> <span begin="1:42.483" end="1:42.731">why</span> <span begin="1:42.731" end="1:42.905">you</span> <span begin="1:42.905" end="1:43.148">had</span> <span begin="1:43.148" end="1:43.415">to</span> <span begin="1:43.415" end="1:43.871">move</span> <span begin="1:43.871" end="1:45.216">away</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">这便是你执意离去的缘由</span></p><p begin="1:45.929" end="1:48.348" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="1:45.929" end="1:46.106">When</span> <span begin="1:46.106" end="1:46.577">people</span> <span begin="1:46.577" end="1:46.912">ask</span> <span begin="1:46.912" end="1:47.154">that&apos;s</span> <span begin="1:47.154" end="1:47.576">what</span> <span begin="1:47.576" end="1:47.830">I</span> <span begin="1:47.830" end="1:48.348">say</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">若有人问起，我便以此为由</span></p><p begin="1:48.420" end="1:52.636" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="1:48.420" end="1:48.602">But</span> <span begin="1:48.602" end="1:48.785">they</span> <span begin="1:48.785" end="1:49.871">know</span> <span begin="1:49.871" end="1:50.192">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="1:50.757" end="1:52.636">lying</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">可他们都知道，我不过是自己骗自己</span></p><p begin="1:54.424" end="1:59.955" itunes:key="L18" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="1:54.424" end="1:54.703">I</span> <span begin="1:54.703" end="1:54.944">don&apos;t</span> <span begin="1:54.944" end="1:55.149">know</span> <span begin="1:55.149" end="1:55.616">who</span> <span begin="1:55.616" end="1:56.187">lives</span> <span begin="1:56.187" end="1:56.881">in</span> <span begin="1:57.244" end="1:58.170">these</span> <span begin="1:58.170" end="1:59.955">houses</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我不知道如今是谁住进了这些房子</span></p><p begin="2:01.363" end="2:04.444" itunes:key="L19" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="2:01.363" end="2:01.545">But</span> <span begin="2:01.545" end="2:01.699">you</span> <span begin="2:01.699" end="2:02.331">still</span> <span begin="2:02.331" end="2:02.635">live</span> <span begin="2:02.635" end="2:03.215">inside</span> <span begin="2:03.215" end="2:03.363">of</span> <span begin="2:03.363" end="2:03.480">my</span> <span begin="2:03.480" end="2:04.444">head</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">可你依旧住在我的脑海深处</span></p><p begin="2:09.202" end="2:14.982" itunes:key="L20" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="2:09.202" end="2:09.503">You</span> <span begin="2:09.503" end="2:09.979">didn&apos;t</span> <span begin="2:09.979" end="2:10.397">leave</span> <span begin="2:10.397" end="2:10.737">me</span> <span begin="2:10.882" end="2:12.032">much</span> <span begin="2:12.032" end="2:12.658">but</span> <span begin="2:12.658" end="2:12.813">the</span> <span begin="2:12.813" end="2:13.793">things</span> <span begin="2:13.793" end="2:14.331">you</span> <span begin="2:14.331" end="2:14.982">said</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你没给我留下什么，唯有那些说过的话</span></p><p begin="2:17.811" end="2:23.989" itunes:key="L21" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="2:17.811" end="2:18.061">They</span> <span begin="2:18.061" end="2:19.414">stayed,</span> <span begin="2:21.457" end="2:21.745">they</span> <span begin="2:21.745" end="2:23.989">stayed</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">挥之不去，长留心间</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="2:19.608" end="2:21.264"><span begin="2:19.608" end="2:19.938">(The</span> <span begin="2:19.938" end="2:21.264">stayed)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">声声在耳</span></span></p><p begin="2:29.565" end="2:36.612" itunes:key="L22" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="2:29.565" end="2:30.305">I</span> <span begin="2:30.305" end="2:31.192">still</span> <span begin="2:31.192" end="2:32.151">see</span> <span begin="2:32.151" end="2:32.788">you,</span> <span begin="2:33.213" end="2:33.832">you</span> <span begin="2:33.970" end="2:34.859">still</span> <span begin="2:34.859" end="2:35.972">see</span> <span begin="2:35.972" end="2:36.612">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我任能望见你，你也仍能望见我</span></p><p begin="2:37.624" end="2:42.070" itunes:key="L23" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="2:37.624" end="2:37.819">But</span> <span begin="2:37.819" end="2:38.132">we</span> <span begin="2:38.132" end="2:38.611">don&apos;t</span> <span begin="2:38.611" end="2:39.369">see</span> <span begin="2:39.369" end="2:39.748">each</span> <span begin="2:39.748" end="2:40.557">other</span> <span begin="2:40.557" end="2:42.070">anymore</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">只是我们，再也不会真正相见</span></p><p begin="2:44.292" end="2:51.590" itunes:key="L24" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="2:44.292" end="2:45.019">I</span> <span begin="2:45.019" end="2:46.143">still</span> <span begin="2:46.143" end="2:47.018">love</span> <span begin="2:47.018" end="2:47.539">you,</span> <span begin="2:47.923" end="2:48.711">you</span> <span begin="2:48.711" end="2:49.751">still</span> <span begin="2:49.751" end="2:50.714">love</span> <span begin="2:50.714" end="2:51.590">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我依然深爱着你，你也对我亦有余情</span></p><p begin="2:52.627" end="2:56.884" itunes:key="L25" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="2:52.627" end="2:52.847">We</span> <span begin="2:52.847" end="2:53.512">can&apos;t</span> <span begin="2:53.512" end="2:53.852">love</span> <span begin="2:53.852" end="2:54.494">each</span> <span begin="2:54.494" end="2:55.058">other</span> <span begin="2:55.379" end="2:56.884">anymore</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">可我们再也不能彼此相爱</span></p><p begin="2:57.847" end="2:58.883" itunes:key="L26" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="2:57.847" end="2:58.283">Can</span> <span begin="2:58.283" end="2:58.883">we?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">不是吗?</span></p><p begin="3:30.389" end="3:35.906" itunes:key="L27" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:30.389" end="3:30.713">I</span> <span begin="3:30.713" end="3:30.915">don&apos;t</span> <span begin="3:30.915" end="3:31.625">believe</span> <span begin="3:31.625" end="3:31.949">in</span> <span begin="3:31.949" end="3:34.016">haunted</span> <span begin="3:34.016" end="3:35.906">houses</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我从不相信世上真有鬼屋</span></p><p begin="3:37.354" end="3:40.750" itunes:key="L28" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="3:37.354" end="3:37.535">But</span> <span begin="3:37.535" end="3:37.708">I</span> <span begin="3:37.708" end="3:38.228">still</span> <span begin="3:38.228" end="3:38.598">see</span> <span begin="3:38.598" end="3:38.847">you</span> <span begin="3:38.847" end="3:39.221">there</span> <span begin="3:39.221" end="3:39.374">on</span> <span begin="3:39.374" end="3:39.578">the</span> <span begin="3:39.578" end="3:40.750">bed</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">可我却依旧总瞥见你在床畔安眠</span></p><p begin="3:45.158" end="3:51.289" itunes:key="L29" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:45.158" end="3:45.435">I</span> <span begin="3:45.435" end="3:45.710">wish</span> <span begin="3:45.710" end="3:45.897">I</span> <span begin="3:45.897" end="3:46.644">hadn&apos;t</span> <span begin="3:46.644" end="3:47.376">said</span> <span begin="3:48.005" end="3:48.626">all</span> <span begin="3:48.626" end="3:48.799">the</span> <span begin="3:48.799" end="3:49.769">things</span> <span begin="3:49.769" end="3:50.355">I</span> <span begin="3:50.355" end="3:51.289">said</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我多希望，当初未曾说出那些追悔莫及的话语</span></p></div></body></tt>